  <bioghist id="aspace_f5297d6b6e8b45820e5ae2304c5c64ca">
    <head>BIOGRAPHICAL NOTE</head>
<p>Henderson was the Assistant Secretary of the Board of Indian Commissioners. McDowell was Secretary of the Board of Indian Commissioners. Burke was commissioner of the Office of Indian Affairs.</p>  </bioghist>
